#=================================================================================================================================
#
#	<0000>		Exiled Filter : Made For Path of Exile
#
#=================================================================================================================================
#
#	Always set borders as highlight to pick.
#	Borders' Color will follow the item's rarity.
#	Valuable items and currencies will also set alert sound, make sure you have turn the filter sound on.
#	
#	Made by Jimmyee Kao since 2017/06/26
#	Updated to Harbinger League.
#
